Title: Paper Clip (3)
Plot: A.D. Skinner and Scully are at a standoff when Mulder bursts in and discovers that Skinner has the digital tape. Reunited, Mulder and Scully travel to a secret vault inside a mine and find an elaborate filing system of medical records which reveals that Mulder's sister may not have been the first choice for abduction. Meanwhile, Skinner deals with the Cigarette-Smoking Man for their safety.
GuestStars: Walter Gotell, Melinda McGraw, Robert Lewis, Lenno Britos, Martin Evans, Peta Brookstone, Stanley Walsh, John Moore
